data.description: ***Ask about the possibility of receiving 1% reduction in interest rate and free refi.*** Welcome to the serene 55+ community of Liberty Cottages in Park West, where comfort meets elegance in this spacious home nestled along the picturesque marsh. Step onto the charming front porch, where the allure of this residence begins. Inside, discover a blend of sophistication and comfort, with exquisite wide plank flooring, plantation shutters, and crown molding that add a touch of refinement to the interiors, all bathed in abundant natural light.The heart of the home, the family room, beckons with its generous space and a warm fireplace, perfect for cozy gatherings. Transition seamlessly into the inviting formal dining room that leads to the well-appointed kitchen,boasting stainless steel appliances, sleek granite countertops, and ample cabinetry. The large island invites casual dining, complemented by a butler's pantry for added convenience. Adjacent is an inviting eat-in area that opens to the expansive enclosed porch and backyard, offering a tranquil wooded view that extends to the serene marsh beyond.  Indulge in the tranquility of the owner's suite, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and double doors that lead to the ensuite bath, featuring a dual sink vanity and a luxurious step-in shower. Two additional bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a convenient half bathroom cater to guests and daily living needs.  Venture to the second level and discover a versatile large bonus room or additional bedroom with a full bathroom, providing ample space for hobbies, relaxation, or hosting guests. With a backyard offering the beauty of nature and the calming presence of the marsh, this home offers a truly idyllic setting for peaceful living.  Seize the opportunity to become a part of this vibrant 55+ community and embrace the comfort and elegance that this meticulously maintained home has to offer. Schedule your showing today before this exceptional opportunity slips away.
